snippet.title: Longplay of Carl Lewis Athletics 2000
snippet.description:
Longplay of Carl Lewis Athletics 2000, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Color. This game's version was released on Sep. 15th, 2000. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00​ - Start
16:02 - Bronze Medal
28:55 - Silver Medal
41:15 - Gold Medal
41:28 - Credits

By: Terua
